{"word":"δελεάζω","slug":"δελεάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δελεάζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δέλεαρ'><el>δέλεαρ</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to entice</i> or <i>catch by a bait</i>: — <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> cogn., <el>νῶτον ὑὸς περὶ ἄγκιστρον δ.</el> <i>to put</i> it on the hook <i>as a bait</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}